2_382 peːMgvinapakSirAːjasya zarIːrasya uccatAː dvOː hastOː Soːxaza ca aMwgulayoː Bavati .
2_383 asya zarIːrasya parimAːNaM paYcacatvAːriMzatkiloːgrAːmamitaM Bavati .
2_384 eːSaH pakSIː prAːyaH jaleː eːva nivasati .
2_385 tatra sa mIːnAːn KAːditvAː svajIːvanaM yAːpayati .
2_386 paraM strIː- peːMgvinapakSIː BUːmOː himasya vAː upari dveː trIːNi vAː aNxAːni sUːteː .
2_387 tatrEːva aNxeːByaH peːMgvinapakSizAːvakAːH utpadyanteː .
2_388 yadAː peːMgvinapakSiNaH aNxAːni poːSayituM BUːmOː vasanti tadAː teː vizAːlAːn nIːxAːlayAːn racayanti .
2_389 pratyeːkaM nIːxAːlayeː prAːyaH dazalakSAːNi peːMgvinapakSiNoː vasanti .
2_390 tasya strIː himasyoːpari keːvalam eːkameːva aNxaM sUːteː sapadi ca samudraM prati nivartateː .
2_391 pumAːn peːMgvinapakSIː svazAːvakasya udBavaparyantamaNxaM seːvateː .
2_392 sa tadaNxaM svapAːdayoːH samIːpeː kRtvAː svazarIːrasya aDoːBAːgeːna AːvRtya tiSVati .
2_393 tadAː saH anyaH aneːkEːH puMBiH peːMgvinapakSiBiH sAːkaM mAːsadvayaparyantam aNxaM seːvamAːnaH tiSVati .
2_394 eːtasmin antarAːleː sa kiYcidapi na KAːdati .
2_395 ahoː pitRvAːtsalyam!.
2_396 sa svamuKeːna eːtat poːSaNa kAːryaM sampAːdayati .
2_397 yadAː peːMgvinapakSizAːvakAːH prAːdurBavanti tadAː teːSAːM mAːtaraH sstrIːpeːMgvinapakSiNaH nIːxAːlayam AːgacCanti svazAːvakAːnAːM ca rakSaNeː tatparAː Bavanti .
2_398 saH peːMgvinapakSiNaH samudraM prati gacCanti.
2_399 teː AːtmanaH svazAːvakAːnAːM ca kRteː KAːdyam anviSyanti.
2_400 triByaH saptAːheːByaH anantaraM teː BoːjanamAːdAːya pratyAːvartanteː .
2_401 prOːXAːH peːMgvinapakSiNaH zAːvakeːByaH uSNatAːM dAːtuM tAːn paritaH SaxmAːsAːn tiSqanti .
2_402 SaxBiH mAːsEːH peːMgvinapakSizAːvakAːH samyag rUːpeːNa puSqAːH AːtmarakSAːM ca kartuM samarTAːH Bavanti .
2_403 tasmin grAːmeː zrIːpatiH nAːma kRSIːvalaH vasati sma .
2_404 grAːmeː vartateː zrIːviVValasya mandiram .
2_405 zrIːpatiH zrIːviVValaH paramaBaktaH asti .
2_406 saH pratidinaM zrIːviVValasya pUːjanaM karoːti, BajanaM karoːti ca .
2_407 sa pratidinaM vadati - zrIːviValaH mama cintAːM kuryAːt mama kSeːmaM sAːDayeːt .
2_408 mayAː kimapi karttavyaM na vidyateː .
2_409 zrIːviVValaH eːva mama trAːtAː rakSaNakartAː ca iti .
