2_539 tava pitAː kaH .
2_540 nivAːsasTAːnaM kutra .
2_541 eːtAːdRzam uttaram AːsIːt paramanirBIːkasya paYcadazavarSIːyasya bAːlakasya candrazeːKara-AːjAːdasya .
2_542 aneːna uttareːNa krudDaH AːwglanyAːyaDIːzaH tasmEː paYcadazavAːraMveːtrAːGAːtm AːdiSqavAːn .
